import React, {useEffect,useState} from 'react'; import API from '../api'; export default function Grades(){ const [grades,setGrades]=useState([]); useEffect(()=>{ API.get('/grades').then(r=>setGrades(r.data)).catch(()=>setGrades([])); },[]); return (

Grades

{grades.map((g,i)=>(
{g.assignment_title} - {g.grade ?? 'Pending'}
))}
) }
